01:42.510 --> 01:45.849
Danny, this is the best gift I could get.

01:45.849 --> 01:48.502
I didn't think you'd come 
back from Florida in time.

01:48.502 --> 01:51.000
Hey, anything for my nana.

01:57.533 --> 01:59.431
This guy's still at it?

01:59.431 --> 02:02.583
I'm gonna put his head in that 
squeeze box he doesn't shut up.

02:02.583 --> 02:05.789
Shut your mouth, punk.
I love that tune.

02:05.789 --> 02:07.928
Don't screw with me, old man.

02:07.928 --> 02:09.995
Or what?

02:10.268 --> 02:12.066
You sit down and drink your Shirley Temple.

02:12.066 --> 02:15.540
You sit down before I rip your 
finger off and shove it up your...

02:16.225 --> 02:17.702
Get down!

02:24.571 --> 02:26.298
Ma, you all right?

02:26.298 --> 02:29.614
Danny, did you...
Oh, my God.!

